{"word":"πέλας","slug":"πέλας","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πέλας</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>near, hard by, close</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>like <el>ἐγγύς</el>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <el>χριμφθεὶς πέλας</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; <el>π. στείχειν, παρεῖναι, στῆναι</el> <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>οἱ πέλας</el> (<a href='S:scilicet'>sc.</a> <el>ὄντες</el>) <i>one's neighbours</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: hence <i>one's fellow-creatures, all men</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b>: in sg., <el>ὁ πέλας</el> <i>one's neighbour, any man</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}